      The Department of Developmental Services maintains this Web site as
     a service to the people of California. If you would like additional
   information about California's developmental disability service system,
      we suggest you contact your local regional center. If you have a
        problem or would like to submit comments or suggestions about
    California's developmental disability service system, please see our
                    Appeals, Complaints & Comments page.

    If you have technical problems viewing any of the pages contained on
    this Web site, or would like to submit comments or suggestions about
               this site, please E-mail the DDS Webmaster at:

                              ddsweb@dds.ca.gov

    This site was designed to be viewed using all the major Web browsers.
     It is best viewed with a browser that support tables and JavaScript
   such as Netscape Navigator or Microsoft Internet Explorer versions 3.0
    or higher. The view is also better with a monitor set at a resolution
                     of 800x600 and High Color (16 bit).
